verbose_text: XREF_BIBR CaSR couples to heterotrimeric G proteins (Galpha 11) and the adaptor related protein complex-2 sigma-subunit (AP2sigma) to mediate signaling via intracellular Ca 2+ (Ca 2+ i) mobilization and mitogen activated protein kinases.
